<div class="flex flex-col gap-8 h-[500px] justify-center items-start">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight">Build your component library</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground">Unstyled and styled UI components built with web components.<br/> Accessible, customizable, and framework-agnostic.</p>	
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-row gap-4 items-center">
    <a href="/docs/components/accordion">
      <button class="bg-foreground text-background text-[0.8rem] tracking-[-0.005rem] font-medium rounded px-4 py-2 transition-colors hover:bg-muted-foreground hover:text-background">Get Started</button>
